nodes.text: Glynnis Talken Campbell (born June 12, 1957) voiced Salla Zend, Vima-Da-Boda and Jem Ysanna in the Dark Empire audio dramas and Nomi Sunrider in the Tales of the Jedi: Dark Lords of the Sith audio drama. She is perhaps best known for voicing Sarah Kerrigan in the computer game StarCraft.
